<heading bold="true" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
Clé d’identification des espèces malgaches de 
<taxonomicName box="[183,292,300,328]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Deparia</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="359" type="key">
<key pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyStep pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,790,346,532]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
1. Fronde entièrement couverte de poils très fins, de 
<quantity box="[694,790,347,371]" metricMagnitude="-5" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" unit="mm" value="0.02">0,02 mm</quantity>
de diamètre formant un tomentum ± dense sur les axes et le limbe; sores linéaires ................................ 
<taxonomicName box="[655,787,410,434]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="florensiae">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[655,787,410,434]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">D. florensiae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,790,346,532]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
1a. Fronde à limbe glabre; poils sur les axes de la fronde, plus gros, de 
<quantity box="[265,419,475,499]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.05" metricValueMax="1.5" metricValueMin="0.6" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" unit="mm" value="0.105" valueMax="0.15" valueMin="0.06">0,06-0,15 mm</quantity>
de diamètre, épars; sores ronds ... ....................................................................................... 2
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,788,572,693]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="359">2. Limbe 1–penné; costae des pennes moyennes ailées sur toute leur longueur ....................................................... 3</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,788,572,693]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="359">2a. Limbe 2–penné; costae des pennes moyennes non ailées ou à aile étroite, discontinue ......................................... 5</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,789,733,854]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
3. Rachis écailleux et pileux avec des écailles et des poils longs de 
<quantity box="[209,296,765,789]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" unit="mm" value="3.0" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="2.0">2-4 mm</quantity>
............................................... 
<taxonomicName box="[640,788,765,789]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longipilosa">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[640,788,765,789]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">D. longipilosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,789,733,854]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
3a. Rachis non écailleux, glabre ou avec des poils très courts, longs de 
<quantity box="[272,400,830,854]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.9999999999999996" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" unit="mm" value="0.39999999999999997" valueMax="0.7" valueMin="0.1">0,1-0,7 mm</quantity>
.................................................... 4
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,789,894,1111]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
4. Pennes moyennes pinnatifides à pinnatipartites; lobes des pennes à apex presque toujours tronqué, à marge apicale crénelée et marges latérales sinueuses à entières .............. ............................................................. 
<taxonomicName box="[600,787,990,1014]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="septentrionalis">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[600,621,991,1014]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">D</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[633,787,990,1014]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">septentrionalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,789,894,1111]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
4a. Pennes moyennes pinnatiséquées; lobes des pennes à apex non tronqué, à marge crénée sur toute leur longueur ....... .................................................................... 
<taxonomicName box="[653,787,1087,1111]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="parvisora">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[653,787,1087,1111]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">D. parvisora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,790,1152,1530]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
5. Costae non ailées; pinnules des pennes moyennes pinnatiséquées; fond du sinus entre deux lobes ultimes en forme de ‘U’; deux 
<typeStatus box="[387,443,1217,1241]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">types</typeStatus>
de poils sur la face adaxiale des nervures: des poils vermiculaires, courts (
<quantity box="[623,754,1248,1273]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" unit="mm" value="0.3" valueMax="0.5" valueMin="0.1">0,1-0,5 mm</quantity>
) et quelques poils plus longs (
<quantity box="[457,588,1281,1305]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.25" metricValueMax="1.8" metricValueMin="0.7" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" unit="mm" value="1.25" valueMax="1.8" valueMin="0.7">0,7-1,8 mm</quantity>
), apprimés, aplatis, annelés, à cellules courtes et apex émoussé .... 
<taxonomicName box="[667,784,1312,1336]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="boryana">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[667,784,1312,1336]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">D. boryana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,790,1152,1530]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
5a. Costae le plus souvent étroitement ailées, à aile discontinue, large de 
<quantity box="[278,414,1377,1401]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" unit="mm" value="0.2" valueMax="0.3" valueMin="0.1">0,1-0,3 mm</quantity>
; pinnules des pennes moyennes pinnatifides à pinnatipartites; fond du sinus entre deux lobes ultimes en forme de ‘V’; un seul 
<typeStatus box="[634,683,1442,1466]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">type</typeStatus>
de poils, vermiculaires, courts (
<quantity box="[420,554,1474,1498]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" metricValueMax="5.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" unit="mm" value="0.3" valueMax="0.5" valueMin="0.1">0,1-0,5 mm</quantity>
) sur la face adaxialee des nervures ......................................... 
<taxonomicName box="[611,785,1506,1530]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Cornopteris" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="marojejyensis">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[611,785,1506,1530]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">D. marojejyensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
</key>
