<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="359" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[139,790,1796,1949]" lastBlockId="2.[827,1477,282,435]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">
<emphasis box="[177,243,1797,1820]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">Notes.</emphasis>
– Le 
<typeStatus box="[313,361,1796,1820]" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">type</typeStatus>
du genre 
<taxonomicName box="[478,565,1797,1820]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[478,565,1797,1820]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">Deparia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
est désigné comme 
<taxonomicName box="[139,255,1829,1852]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macraei">
<emphasis box="[139,255,1829,1852]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">D. macraei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
lors de sa description par W.J. Hooker et R.K. Greville en 1829. Les auteurs remarquent par la suite que 
<taxonomicName box="[139,327,1892,1916]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dicksoniaceae" genus="Dicksonia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Cyatheales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="prolifera">
<emphasis box="[139,327,1892,1916]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">Dicksonia prolifera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
publié en 1824 doit être placé en synonyme sous 
<taxonomicName box="[192,360,1925,1948]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macraei">
<emphasis box="[192,360,1925,1948]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">Deparia macraei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Ils rectifient la typification du genre en publiant la nouvelle combinaison 
<taxonomicName box="[1170,1339,282,306]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="prolifera">
<emphasis box="[1170,1339,282,306]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">Deparia prolifera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
qui a priorité sur 
<taxonomicName box="[866,975,315,338]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Athyriaceae" genus="Deparia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macraei">
<emphasis box="[866,975,315,338]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">D. macraei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Cette rectification est publiée dans l’« addenda et corrigenda » du deuxième volume de l’ 
<emphasis box="[1269,1404,346,370]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="359">Icones filicum</emphasis>
. Cette dernière partie est probablement publiée en 1832 (
<bibRefCitation author="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; R. S. Cowan" journalOrPublisher="Bohn, Scheltma &amp; Holkema" pageId="2" pageNumber="359" refId="ref10819" refString="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; R. S. Cowan (1979). Taxonomic literature: H-Le. Vol. 2. 2 nd ed. Bohn, Scheltma &amp; Holkema" title="Taxonomic literature: H-Le. Vol. 2. 2 nd ed." type="book" year="1979">Stafleu &amp; Cowan, 1979</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
